description: Mayo and Mustard serves hot & fresh, made-to-order sandwiches.We are a new gourmet food truck offering delicious hot deli-style sandwiches to the Bay Area. Our mission is to spread the “Mayo & Mustard sandwich experience” and captivate the appetites of those who love sandwiches. We put our love into every sandwich we make.Learn more about where our truck will be stationed next by finding us using the Roaming Hunger app!
name: Mayo & Mustard
